i": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031326_1109469676539289_4268533616333460252_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=h0dZF29gDYgQ7kNvgFsXU-I&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBw8vbKdPsQB7j3nfliYzcgX4tkWwTRbu9rqBr2I5stnw&oe=671773F7"}, {"file_name": "Final2.png", "id": "916532898880837", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003274_916532902214170_6367672695544734699_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=G4XlYsYODFcQ7kNvgH4BNkD&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBQDE9JCT-XITS_yDI8DlA0SJvV2w3dfJUpJHq9v4lPNA&oe=67179C3A"}, {"file_name": "Final3.png", "id": "1165340330878993", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974677_1165340334212326_9147485654240656059_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FzL9O-zRg4QQ7kNvgGQKf7W&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC0BLqEe2jn-43wJjwQdsQpQDdZMasu_DIGgohPWGxZjw&oe=67177707"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Light Up The Dark", "keywords": [], "long_description": "*  Finger Controls.  \"Play\" the fireworks with your right-hand fingers using individual fingers and \"chords\" of fingers to fire different types of fire works.\n*  The Color Ball.  Your left hand is the color ball, moving side-to-side changes the color of the firework, and up/down adjusts the size of the fireworks blasts.\n*  Seamlessly switch between hands and controllers (with a hardware delay).\n*  Play reclined or laying down!  Or upside down.  Any position, any space.\n*  Environmental features such as snow, falling leaves, fireflies, and bubbles.  Seriously, try the bubbles.\n*  Listen to various audio tracks including a gentle Mozart piece, a Sousa March, and Wagner's Ride of the Valkyries, adjustable volumes for music and fireworks.\n*  Set the weather and the Speed of Time.  Note, the weather has a mind of its own.  \n*  Show and hide individual UI components or 